Oceania is the eighth studio album by American alternative rock band 
The Smashing Pumpkins, released on June 19, 2012 on EMI and Martha's 
Music. Produced by Billy Corgan and Bjorn Thorsrud, the album is part 
of the band's ongoing 44-song box set, Teargarden by Kaleidyscope. As 
of September 2012, Oceania has sold over 102,000 copies in the US.
